<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Email Template</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./activation-mail.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <table
      role="presentation"
      border="0"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      class="body"
    >
      <tr>
        <td class="container-fluid">
          <div class="content">
            <div class="header">
              <img
                src="https://iffigoa.org/backend/assets/images/IFFI-Whte-Logo.png"
                alt="alt text"
                height="87px"
                width="100px"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="imgShows">
              <img
                src="https://iffigoa.org/backend/assets/images/emailBanner.png"
                alt="alt text"
                height="87px"
                width="100px"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="welNote">
              <h4>Welcome to the International Film Festival of India!</h4>
            </div>
            <hr />
            <table
              class="msg"
              style="border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0px 12px"
            >
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <p>Hi <%= clientName %>!</p>
                    <p>We are excited to have you onboard.</p>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 0">
                      Thank you for registering for the International Film
                      Festival of India (IFFI) Goa. Here are your details of
                      registration.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <table>
                      <tr>
                        <td>
                          <p style="margin: 0">Name</p>
                        </td>
                        <td>
                          <p style="margin: 0">:</p>
                        </td>
                        <td style="padding-left: 4px">
                          <p style="margin: 0"><%= clientName %></p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td>
                          <p style="margin: 0">Email ID</p>
                        </td>
                        <td>
                          <p style="margin: 0">:</p>
                        </td>
                        <td style="padding-left: 4px">
                          <p style="margin: 0"><%= clientEmail %></p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td>
                          <p style="margin: 0">Location</p>
                        </td>
                        <td>
                          <p style="margin: 0">:</p>
                        </td>
                        <td style="padding-left: 4px">
                          <p style="margin: 0">Goa,India</p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <p style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px">
                      <span
                        >You can find more information about the festival,
                        including the schedule and venues, on our website.</span
                      >
                      <span></span>
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <br /><br />

                <tr>
                  <td style="text-align: center">
                    <a
                      href="https://www.iffigoa.org/festival/"
                      class="primary-btn"
                      >Visit Now</a
                    >
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <br /><br />
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <br />
                    <p style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px">
                      <span>Best regards,</span>
                      <span>The IFFI Team</span>
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>

            <table
              style="
                border-collapse: separate;
                border-spacing: 0px 12px;
                padding: 0 15px;
              "
            >
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <div class="social-link">
                    <a href=""
                      ><svg
                        fill="currentColor"
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        viewBox="0 0 512 512"
                      >
                        <path
                          d="M512 256C512 114.6 397.4 0 256 0S0 114.6 0 256C0 376 82.7 476.8 194.2 504.5V334.2H141.4V256h52.8V222.3c0-87.1 39.4-127.5 125-127.5c16.2 0 44.2 3.2 55.7 6.4V172c-6-.6-16.5-1-29.6-1c-42 0-58.2 15.9-58.2 57.2V256h83.6l-14.4 78.2H287V510.1C413.8 494.8 512 386.9 512 256h0z"
                        /></svg
                    ></a>
                    <a href=""
                      ><svg
                        fill="currentColor"
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        viewBox="0 0 512 512"
                      >
                        <path
                          d="M389.2 48h70.6L305.6 224.2 487 464H345L233.7 318.6 106.5 464H35.8L200.7 275.5 26.8 48H172.4L272.9 180.9 389.2 48zM364.4 421.8h39.1L151.1 88h-42L364.4 421.8z"
                        /></svg
                    ></a>
                    <a href=""
                      ><svg
                        fill="currentColor"
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        viewBox="0 0 448 512"
                      >
                        <path
                          d="M224.1 141c-63.6 0-114.9 51.3-114.9 114.9s51.3 114.9 114.9 114.9S339 319.5 339 255.9 287.7 141 224.1 141zm0 189.6c-41.1 0-74.7-33.5-74.7-74.7s33.5-74.7 74.7-74.7 74.7 33.5 74.7 74.7-33.6 74.7-74.7 74.7zm146.4-194.3c0 14.9-12 26.8-26.8 26.8-14.9 0-26.8-12-26.8-26.8s12-26.8 26.8-26.8 26.8 12 26.8 26.8zm76.1 27.2c-1.7-35.9-9.9-67.7-36.2-93.9-26.2-26.2-58-34.4-93.9-36.2-37-2.1-147.9-2.1-184.9 0-35.8 1.7-67.6 9.9-93.9 36.1s-34.4 58-36.2 93.9c-2.1 37-2.1 147.9 0 184.9 1.7 35.9 9.9 67.7 36.2 93.9s58 34.4 93.9 36.2c37 2.1 147.9 2.1 184.9 0 35.9-1.7 67.7-9.9 93.9-36.2 26.2-26.2 34.4-58 36.2-93.9 2.1-37 2.1-147.8 0-184.8zM398.8 388c-7.8 19.6-22.9 34.7-42.6 42.6-29.5 11.7-99.5 9-132.1 9s-102.7 2.6-132.1-9c-19.6-7.8-34.7-22.9-42.6-42.6-11.7-29.5-9-99.5-9-132.1s-2.6-102.7 9-132.1c7.8-19.6 22.9-34.7 42.6-42.6 29.5-11.7 99.5-9 132.1-9s102.7-2.6 132.1 9c19.6 7.8 34.7 22.9 42.6 42.6 11.7 29.5 9 99.5 9 132.1s2.7 102.7-9 132.1z"
                        /></svg
                    ></a>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p
                    class="disclose"
                    style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem"
                  >
                    <span style="font-weight: 500; color: #202020"
                      >DISCLAIMER CLAUSE</span
                    >
                    <span
                      >The contents of e-mail message including attachment/s is
                      confidential and is intended only for the named
                      recipient(s) above and contains information that is
                      privileged, proprietary or exempt from disclosure under
                      the applicable laws. The information contained in this
                      e-mail including the attachment/of the content is being
                      provided to you for the specific purpose of evaluation. No
                      legal consequences can be derived of this e-mail. Should
                      you receive this message by mistake, you are hereby
                      notified that any unauthorized use, dissemination,
                      distribution or reproduction of this e-mail message,
                      including attachment/s is strictly prohibited unless
                      authorized in writing by us. If you have received this
                      message in error, and/or are not an intended recipient
                      please notify the sender forthwith and delete this email
                      message including attachments from your computer. Neither
                      the sender nor NFDC shall accept any liability for any
                      damage from the use and/or acceptance of this email.</span
                    >
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <div style="text-align: center">
                    <img
                      src="https://iffigoa.org/backend/assets/images/azadi-ka-mahotsav.png"
                      alt="alt text"
                      height="100px"
                      width="250px"
                    />
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
